## Version 1.0

- MAC Adapter with sensible interface
- Defaults module for default adapters for core functions
- Streaming hash and MAC functions (can we use Elixir Stream?)
- Tests for main interface
- Revised docs and doctests

## Post Version 1.0

- Handle Blake3
- Handle SHA3 and Blake2
- Dialixyr
- Key generate functions for minimal entropy (e.g. 2^64)
- Full PKCS suite
